title: Ep. 456 - Angry Young Man  - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Champaklal asks Jethalal about the reason for his irritation. The gents of society are worried about the fight between Jethalal and Popatlal. Jethalal even shouts on Daya and shows his irritation on her. Champaklal is worried for Jethalal.

title: Ep. 457 - Jethalal Is Upset - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha is upset as he doesn't get the order. His shows his anger on Popatlal and Bhide. Daya wishes for the situation to be normal. Later, Jetha realises his mistake and apologizes.

title: Ep. 458 - Daya's Vow To Not Play Garba - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya, in view of Jetha's order, has taken a vow to not play Garba. The people in the society also end up leaving as Daya isn't ready to play Garba.

title: Ep. 459 - John Abraham In Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha comes up with an idea to make sure that he gets the deal. The fate's in Jetha's favor. Later, everybody plays Garba when John Abraham pays a visit.

title: Ep. 460 - Chachaji Is Proud Of Jetha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Chachaji gets to know about the deal that Jetha finalized. He's proud of the fact that Jetha has cracked the deal despite facing a loss.

title: Ep. 461 - Iyer Plans A Surprise - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha helps Babita and Iyer in finding a ride. They also visit Gada electronics on the way. Later, Babita asks Iyer his plan. Iyer plays smart and doesn't reveal any of his plans.

title: Ep. 462 -  Babita Is Unhappy - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Iyer is in preparation for his anniversary gift for Babita. Meanwhile, Babita is unhappy thinking Iyer has forgotten yet again. She vows she will go back to the mother if he really forgets.

title: Ep. 463 - A Rant Against Husbands - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The wives gather around to buy some vegetables when they start ranting about their husbands. Iyer gets a call from Sodhi about a new car.

title: Ep. 464 - Where Is The Surprise? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: In the morning, Iyer finally gives a huge flower bouquet to Babita that makes her really happy. Meanwhile, Jetha has a really bad dream. But, the surprise still remains a surprise for Babita.

title: Ep. 465 - The Car's Stolen - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The surprise is finally here and Babita is elated. They decide to go on a drive. They reach the temple while a thief steals their car and runs away.

title: Ep. 466 - The Mysterious Car - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Iyer and Babita reach the Police station to register a complaint against the thief. Here, they find out that the car is stolen property. The police doubt them. Sodhi and others come to the rescue while they are also put behind bars.

title: Ep. 467 - Will The Real Thief Be Caught? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal tries finding a way out from the trouble but is of no use. Daya and others are worried as none of them have returned home. Babita tries explaining to the inspector. Meanwhile, Nattu Kaka comes along and tells about Peter Fernandes.

title: Ep. 468 - The Time Is Ticking - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The police have given a time frame to Iyer and others to catch the thief. An ultimatum has been given that if they don't catch the thief in the prescribed time, they will be put behind bars yet again.

title: Ep. 469 - Taarak Comes Up With An Idea - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak comes up with an idea to catch the thief. He narrates his plan to everybody. In the morning, Popatlal does the assigned work and they are confident enough to catch the thief.

title: Ep. 470 - Sodhi Plays Smart - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Peter Fernandes reaches Sodhi's garage. He convinces Sodhi to return the car and is ready to pay him a commission. Meanwhile, they get to know that Peter wouldn't be coming this evening.
